Barn: Gunnar f. 27, Margareta 30, Karin 31, Carl Magnus 36, Per Torsten 41. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 15, med. kand. v. Karol. inst. 19, med. lic. där 24. Tf. aman. v. Sthlms hosp. 21-23, kort. förordn. v. hosp., las. o. san. 22-24, tf. andre und :läk. v. Växjö las. samt assist :läk. v. Hälsingb. las. 24-25, andre o. förste und :läk. v. det sistn. 25-28, prov:läk. i Sorsele distr. samt sjukstuguläk. o. disp :läk. i Sorsele 28-33, järnv:läk. samma tid, prov iläk. i Svendjunga distr. samt sjuks tuguläk. där sed. 33. Led. av komm :fulim. Skr.: smärre upps. i med. o. socialmed. Hobbies: jakt, hund-nppfödn.
translated: Kjellstrand, Torsten Frithiof Magnus, provincial physician, Svenljunga, b. 18/10/97 in Linköping, son of dentist Frithiof K. and Karin Torén. Married on 25/xx to Agda Breimer. Children: Gunnar b. 27, Margareta b. 30, Karin b. 31, Carl Magnus b. 36, Per Torsten b. 41. — High school diploma in Stockholm 15, medical candidate at Karolinska Institute 19, medical degree there in 24. Temporary assistant at Stockholm Hospital 21-23, short-term appointments at hospitals and clinics in 22-24, temporary second assistant physician at Växjö Hospital and assistant physician at Hälsingborg Hospital 24-25, second and first assistant physician at the latter 25-28, provincial physician in Sorsele district and hospital doctor and dispensary physician in Sorsele 28-33, railway physician during the same period, provincial physician in Svenljunga district and hospital doctor there since 33. Member of the county council committee. Writings: minor essays in medicine and social medicine. Hobbies: hunting, breeding dogs.
